}}'''基督城美術館'''（Christchurch Art Gallery Te Puna o Waiwhetū）是[[新西兰|新西兰]][[基督城|基督城]]一家公立美术馆，由{{link-en|基督城议会|Christchurch City Council}}资助。该美術館于2003年5月10日开业 <ref>{{Cite news|title=Grand opening for gallery of wonders|work=Christchurch Star|date=14 May 2003|pages=A4–A5}}</ref>。基督城美術館由布坎集團（Buchan Group）设计<ref>{{Cite web|title=Graham Bennett: Reasons for Voyaging|url=https://christchurchartgallery.org.nz/exhibitions/graham-bennett-reasons-for-voyaging|accessdate=19 May 2019|work=christchurchartgallery.org.nz|archive-date=2020-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220005526/https://christchurchartgallery.org.nz/exhibitions/graham-bennett-reasons-for-voyaging|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

基督城美術館在[[2010年坎特伯雷地震|2010年坎特伯雷地震]]和[[2011年基督城地震|2011年基督城地震]]後被用作[[民防|民防]]总部。在[[2011年基督城地震|2011年基督城地震]]中，基督城美術館受損<ref>Mortimer, Frances (12 October 2014) [http://www.amerisurv.com/content/view/13158/153/ "Not Broken, But Slightly Bowed—Lifting a Landmark Art Gallery in New Zealand"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019113844/http://www.amerisurv.com/content/view/13158/153/|date=19 October 2014}} ''American Surveyor Magazine'' Frederick, Maryland</ref>。由于需要进行大规模的翻新和改进，直到2015年12月19日基督城美術館才重新开放<ref>{{Cite news|author=Gates|first=Charlie|title=Christchurch Art Gallery reopening after nearly 5 years of closure|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/the-press/news/75259288/christchurch-art-gallery-reopening-after-nearly-5-years-of-closure|accessdate=3 January 2016|work=The Press|date=19 December 2015|archive-date=2018-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818215558/https://www.stuff.co.nz/the-press/news/75259288/Christchurch-Art-Gallery-reopening-after-nearly-5-years-of-closure|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

